{"tid":898310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那客批評港商戶沒支那寶 收現金十分落後","createTime":"2018-11-11T15:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T02:23:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5b75729cb96b770ef14b99a076ee030455f69de1","tid":898310,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:03:28.000Z","msg":"內地遊客劉小姐和鄭小姐指，報了一天團來香港「自由行」，「報團時是自由行，到香港就叫他帶我們行。」而團費大約200多元。她們又聲稱，由中山到香港，一直有香港導遊、內地導遊相伴。兩人購入了不少生活用品和鞋，認為東涌人流普遍較多。劉小姐批評，香港商戶沒設微信支付、支付寶，指用現金付款十分落後、麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n盧小姐於東涌居住了十多年，同樣留意到最近人流極多，直指心情很差，「全部人沒規矩，席地而坐，買完的東西又隨便放在地上。」<br />\n<br />\n她又指，自己現時會特意繞路，去遠點的商場購買日常用品、吃飯，「以前東薈城幾少人！打橫行都得，而家？俾人碌跛腳！」她又提到違規旅行團問題，批評警方沒有大力執法。"},{"pid":"0ead2f27a1b9e563940ffaea3edb5e4c30a8c8a7","tid":898310,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2079022/org/3f55fbf0a4cfb21cdc75f6e3fe130e63.jpg/WCjiMrV76F834B0_GiQDX8vMAuVgNO9FvUJK9r1CSvY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2079022%2Forg%2F3f55fbf0a4cfb21cdc75f6e3fe130e63.jpg%2FWCjiMrV76F834B0_GiQDX8vMAuVgNO9FvUJK9r1CSvY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e5b1db16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bbdbe92ea4cf0f3d1583f5f35567c24fb66c421","tid":898310,"uid":38194,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"0ead2f27a1b9e563940ffaea3edb5e4c30a8c8a7","tid":898310,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2079022/org/3f55fbf0a4cfb21cdc75f6e3fe130e63.jpg/WCjiMrV76F834B0_GiQDX8vMAuVgNO9FvUJK9r1CSvY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2079022%2Forg%2F3f55fbf0a4cfb21cdc75f6e3fe130e63.jpg%2FWCjiMrV76F834B0_GiQDX8vMAuVgNO9FvUJK9r1CSvY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e5b1db16&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"成班乞兒<img src=\"/assets/fa